    "Factory manuals outline information on machine operation, safety protocols, quality assurance, and more.",
    "These resources, provided by factory management teams, initialize the knowledge base for each specific factory.",
    "The materials come in various formats, including PDF, Word, and CSV files.",
    "In addition to the factory manuals, we integrate issue analysis reports from factory workers.",
    "This information is gathered from the production line, utilizing the five-why process, an iterative rootcause analysis technique (Serrat, 2017) (right side of Figure 2)."
